06:51.351 --> 06:52.381
[KNOCK ON DOOR]

06:52.553 --> 06:53.583
Yeah?

06:55.722 --> 06:57.782
Your Honor. I need your help.

06:57.958 --> 07:01.488
-Things get a little backed up in there?
-Heck. no. we had dinner break.

07:02.429 --> 07:04.419
-Already?
-Harry. this guy is amazing.

07:04.598 --> 07:07.428
We practically finished
the whole docket.

07:07.601 --> 07:09.431
But you said you needed my help?

07:09.603 --> 07:11.373
Oh. yeah.

07:11.839 --> 07:14.329
Would you get this knot out for me?

07:15.375 --> 07:17.565
Sure. that's what I'm here for.

07:17.744 --> 07:18.774
[KNOCK ON DOOR]

07:18.946 --> 07:21.176
-Yeah?
-A two-hour dinner break.

07:21.348 --> 07:23.608
-Can you believe it?
-I got time to get some jogging in.

07:23.784 --> 07:25.844
-Pshew. Hi. Harry.
-Hi.

07:26.553 --> 07:30.113
So Mac says things are going okay?

07:30.290 --> 07:31.310
Smooth as silk.

07:31.491 --> 07:34.951
It's amazing how fast things go
when there isn't so much goofing off.

07:36.562 --> 07:40.932
I mean. of course.
goofing off in a professional sense.

07:42.335 --> 07:45.355
-There you go.
-Well. thank you. sir.

07:45.537 --> 07:46.557
Sure.

07:46.738 --> 07:48.728
If you need anything else. I'll be here.

07:48.907 --> 07:51.337
Stapling things to my face.

07:51.509 --> 07:54.379
Well. you have fun. sir.

07:56.248 --> 07:57.268
Your Honor?

07:58.283 --> 08:00.183
Oh. You're busy. I'll be back later.

08:00.352 --> 08:04.352
No. come on in. Selma.
We were just discussing Judge Koppelson.

08:04.521 --> 08:07.251
Aw. What a sweetheart. huh?

08:07.791 --> 08:11.251
Sounds like you're headed for a gang hug.

08:11.762 --> 08:13.732
Go on. tell them.

08:14.098 --> 08:15.658
Tell us what?

08:15.833 --> 08:18.503
Oh. listen.
it's starting to sound like a big deal.

08:18.669 --> 08:19.929
It's no big deal.

08:20.104 --> 08:21.304
What isn't?

08:21.472 --> 08:24.072
I'm going to Florida
and shack up with Marty.

08:25.608 --> 08:26.968
You're getting married?

08:27.509 --> 08:30.709
She doesn't know
what shacking up means?

08:31.813 --> 08:34.613
-Sir. we got a problem.
-Mac. Se|ma's going to Florida.

08:34.783 --> 08:36.383
Be sure to hit Disney World.

08:36.549 --> 08:38.919
-Sir. I'm afraid this is urgent.
-What is it?

08:39.086 --> 08:42.416
I just called a Brooklyn court
to transfer a few grand jury felonies.

08:42.590 --> 08:44.490
Judge Koppelson needed more to do.

08:44.659 --> 08:46.059
From the sound of things...

08:46.227 --> 08:49.857
...he should be able to clean up
the national crime problem by dawn.

08:50.031 --> 08:52.131
MAC: Harry--
-He's not using my gavel. is he?

08:52.300 --> 08:56.430
Harry. there is no Judge Koppelson
in the Brooklyn court.

08:56.604 --> 08:59.514
There's no Judge Koppelson anywhere.

08:59.674 --> 09:01.144
He's a fraud.

09:02.376 --> 09:04.036
Oh. no. I don't believe that.

09:04.210 --> 09:05.610
That's incredible.

09:10.650 --> 09:12.740
I could have told you so.

09:17.357 --> 09:19.347
Yeah. Uh-huh.

09:20.794 --> 09:23.424
Okay. well. thank you.

09:23.596 --> 09:24.616
Any sign of him?

09:24.798 --> 09:27.228
-Dan took him out to dinner.
-ReaHy?

09:27.400 --> 09:30.670
Bull went to the local suck-up eateries
to see if he could find him.

09:30.837 --> 09:31.897
Good thinking.

09:32.706 --> 09:36.106
Well. it turns out our Mr. Koppelson
is with the Brooklyn court system.

09:36.275 --> 09:37.465
Then he is a judge.

09:37.643 --> 09:38.943
Then he is a clerk.

09:39.110 --> 09:40.270
-A clerk?
HARRY: Mm-hm.

09:40.844 --> 09:42.684
In the Records Division. for 35 years.

09:42.846 --> 09:45.506
And he's got a good record.
but he's got no law degree...

09:45.682 --> 09:47.052
...and no college education.

09:47.216 --> 09:48.506
That's incredible.

09:48.683 --> 09:52.983
I mean. this guy just walks in off the street
wearing a robe...

09:53.154 --> 09:56.784
...p|ops himself on the bench.
and everybody falls for it?

09:56.958 --> 09:59.978
-He must think you people are a bunch of....
-Boneheads.

10:01.295 --> 10:03.915
Well. I can see that you're busy.

10:04.098 --> 10:07.118
I'll see you in the cafeteria. bunny rabbit.

10:08.067 --> 10:10.727
